{"tid":1772050,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"底褲中的煙霧餅 - 陳也","createTime":"2019-12-06T10:01:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-06T10:01:50.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f9434ffb860dbf8db08650d01865e0499bf8d102","tid":1772050,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T10:01:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20191206/20819705/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191206%2F20819705%2F&d=3i4OsSLc5DEqZvEdVyqruQmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=c496d3d0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191206%2F20819705%2F&h=5f17b3f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20191206/20819705/</a><br />\n<br />\n底褲中的煙霧餅 - 陳也<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191206/large/1575536198_c8e2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191206%2Flarge%2F1575536198_c8e2.jpg&h=b0824e47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n121，被消失的尖沙嘴煙霧餅在哪裏？<br />\n<br />\n鏡頭下，只見八十歲的雪糕伯伯，無奈歎完黑警TG後，一個人食紅豆雪條。「對呼吸好㗎，身體補返些水。」伯伯老神在在，實牙實齒，雪條如果會講嘢，對白就係：「四點鐘警謊食屎當飯，食支雪條都會屈你手部有動作。」<br />\n<br />\n無影的煙霧餅，到底在哪裏？<br />\n<br />\n在er蛇露出的底褲裏？（難怪雪雪聲，屙尿都射歪）<br />\n<br />\n在荃灣警署黑警向年輕女抗爭者講到明的「強姦房」裏？（因為煙霧大，黑麻麻，睇唔到同袍腹部以下有所動作）<br />\n<br />\n在倒地後被踢頭的暴徒背包裏？（黑警等緊插佢贓）<br />\n<br />\n在popo的海底撈煲底中？（正宗煲底見）<br />\n<br />\n在伍淑清唔見咗的心裏？（黑心煙霧西餅，黑警全家柒折）<br />\n<br />\n在老董的八萬五裏？（唔再提就等於唔存在）<br />\n<br />\n在美國人權法制裁的名單裏？（迅速被中共反制了）<br />\n<br />\n在何已完1.5 cm的傷口裏？（妖！完）<br />\n<br />\n警方煙霧餅與近期笑爆嘴的大媽「dyson泵」之謎，等PK鄧仆街之日，方能破解。 <br />\n<br />\n陳也<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"}]}